#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is the default file manager by &kde;, designed with usability as a "
"primary focus."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; — это инструмент управления файлами в &kde;, удобный и простой в "
"использовании."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
